    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>A simple analytical Susceptible-Infectious-Recovered (SIR) model without vital dynamics is developed from basic assumptions. Based on the data available for the spread of the Covid 19 virus in Italy in 2020, the characteristic parameters of the model are estimated.</jats:p>",
